5) Defendant may not be present where controlled substances are used, packaged for sale, or sold;
6) Defendant to report prescriptions to agent BEFORE filling the prescription;
7) AODA assessment and comply with recommended treatment;
8) Maintain employment of at least 30 hours per week or be a full time student, or a part time student with employment of at least 30 hours per week;
